: your IP address, Open ID and device information, including device ID, platform and Advertising ID and information regarding your use of the LIP Account and LIP-Enabled Service, such as play statistics (e.g. level, heroes, scores, and geographic ranking based on your selected region location).
We use this information to store your LIP Account and LIP-Enabled Service data with your profile and to provide you with feedback and information about your use of the services.
Necessary to perform our contract with you to provide the LIP Account and the LIP-Enabled Service.
