: information about your LIP-Enabled Service activity, such as user ID, Open ID, service activity log, location of the user’s choice, phone memory, device brand, device system version, device manufacturer, ROM, screen resolution, RAM, system time, device model, device ID, device name, CPU model, CPU architecture, app list.
We use this information to ensure that the LIP-Enabled Service is working to enable you to use the LIP-Enabled Service.
Necessary to perform our contract with you to provide the LIP-Enabled Service.
